videos.description: Mississippi State's Lamar Peters shoots a 3 off the fast break and misses but is redeemed by Aric Holman who grabs the offensive rebound and throws it down.
videos.headline: Miss State's Holman redeems missed shot by slamming it down

videos.description: After a steal, Lamar Peters plays it up to Quinndary Weatherspoon who slams it down with two hands to extend Mississippi State's lead over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon extends Bulldogs' early lead with two-handed slam

videos.description: James Daniel III takes the pass from Lamonte Turner and banks the 3-pointer from the Mississippi state logo.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Daniel banks a 3 from ridiculously deep

videos.description: After a Tennessee bad pass, Nick Weatherspoon drives down the court and puts the moves on Tennessee defenders for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Miss State's Weatherspoon gets crafty for and-1

videos.description: Admiral Schofield takes a pass in the post then drives past a defender and hooks a two-point shot while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Schofield sinks a nasty and-1 layup then flexes

videos.description: With time on the shot clock winding down, Jordan Bone puts a last-second spin move on a Bulldog defender then sinks the floater as time expires.
videos.headline: Vols' Bone scores with a slick move as shock clock expires
